---
name: leadbay_refine_prompt
kind: tool-description
short_description: |
  Refine the kind of leads Leadbay surfaces, beyond firmographics (qualitative
  intent, not sector/size). Sets the org's user_prompt and may raise a
  clarification question the composite polls for. Admin-only.
annotations:
  readOnlyHint: false
  destructiveHint: true
  idempotentHint: false
  openWorldHint: true
routing:
  triggers:
    - "focus on companies that <qualitative trait>"
    - "I prefer leads that <behavior/characteristic>"
    - "prioritize companies running their own IT"
    - "deprioritize companies that just raised"
  anti_triggers:
    - phrase: "create a new lens / a lens specialized into <X>"
      route_to: leadbay_new_lens
    - phrase: "add/remove <sector> to/from my <name> lens"
      route_to: leadbay_adjust_audience
    - phrase: "narrow the audience to <sector> / <size>"
      route_to: leadbay_adjust_audience
    - phrase: "show me / list / switch my lenses"
      route_to: leadbay_my_lenses
  prefer_when: "ADMIN-ONLY. Qualitative refinement of the active lens that sector/size can't express. Creating/naming/listing/switching/sector-editing a lens routes elsewhere. Non-admin user → do NOT pick this."
  examples:
    positive:
      - "Focus on hospitals that run their own IT in-house."
      - "Prioritize companies that have recently expanded headcount."
    negative:
      - "Create a lens specialized in automobile."
      - "Add fintech to my Joinery lens."
      - "Show me my lenses."
rendering_hint: |
  On success: confirm the refinement applied to the active lens. If a
  clarification was raised, surface its question (route via ask_user_input_v0).
---
Refine the kind of leads Leadbay surfaces, beyond firmographics. Free-text instruction (e.g. "focus on hospitals running their own IT"). Sets the org's `user_prompt`; if the new prompt produces ambiguous criteria, Leadbay raises a clarification question, which this composite polls for and surfaces. Admin-only on the backend (will return 403 for non-admins).

{{include:headers/tool-when-to-use}} when audience filters (leadbay_adjust_audience) aren't enough.

{{include:headers/tool-when-not-to-use}} to answer a pending clarification — that's leadbay_answer_clarification.

{{include:headers/verification-required-if-write}}
